Source: I001 and `docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-17-quota-presentation-policy.md`, Task 1.

Create `QuotaPresentation.presentProfile(profile, options)` and its pure Node test. The interface returns ordered `{ windowData, label, colorMode }` rows, filters only `visible === false`, preserves duplicate/source order, treats every role equally, and never mutates source state.

Acceptance: the new pure test covers malformed input, role equality, ordering, duplicate IDs, label/colour defaults, and immutability; existing visibility tests remain green.